// 5.105 — **SpringBig Track B Day 9 mobile polish — sticky bottom-nav + 44px touch-targets across the 3 authed `/rewards` pages.** Per `/CODE/Green Life/PLAN_SPRINGBIG_CUTOVER_5_25.md` §4 Day 9 (2026-05-15 deadline shipped early). NEW `app/rewards/RewardsBottomNav.tsx` server component — 3 tabs (🏠 Home / 🎟️ Redeem / 📜 History) wired to `/rewards/dashboard` / `/rewards/redeem` / `/rewards/history`. Active tab highlights indigo-700 + accent underline; inactive tabs stone-500 hover-stone-800. min-h-[56px] tab + min-h-[44px] internal touch targets per Apple HIG. Fixed bottom + max-w-md inner grid + backdrop-blur for the iOS-shrunk-browser-chrome look. 20px page-bottom spacer (h-20) so last content doesn&rsquo;t hide behind the nav. **Wired into:** dashboard `<RewardsBottomNav active="dashboard" />`, redeem `active="redeem"`, history `active="history"`. NotFoundCard variant of dashboard skips nav (no customer record = no redeem/history to nav to; just menu + sign-out CTAs). **Touch-target bump:** Browse-menu button + Sign-out button on dashboard customer + NotFound branches both gain min-h-[44px]; Back-to-dashboard CTAs on redeem + history get the same. **Skipped for v1:** Profile tab (no `/rewards/profile` exists yet — 3-tab grid is cleaner than a placeholder 4th tab). Pull-to-refresh on dashboard (browser-native scroll-up doesn&rsquo;t trigger re-fetch on Server Components — needs a client-component refresh button or a router-refresh handler; deferred to v1 since the existing `revalidate = 0` forces fresh data on every navigation back). 4 files +12 LOC. tsc clean.
